This is the changelog for Calamares. For each release, the major changes and
contributors are listed. Note that Calamares does not have a full historical
changelog -- this log starts with version 3.4.0. See CHANGES-3.3 for the
3.3 series (2022-08 - 2025-07) and CHANGES-3.2 for the history of the 3.2
series (2018-05 - 2022-08).


